ActHazardous Products Act
Precis Regulations amending the CORDED WINDOW COVERING PRODUCTS REGULATIONS specify requirements to reduce the risk of strangulation from corded window covering products. The regulations reference the National Standard of Canada, CAN/CSA-Z600 Safety of Corded Window Covering Products.
